1) Make sure you have installed and are running the deskbar applet, version 2.20 or greater.

2) Right click on the deskbar applet and open up the preferences dialog.

3) Go to the "Searches" tab.

4) Drag n' drop the desktop-plugin-gman.py file inside the list of available searches.

5) Tick on the newly created "G-Man" handler to enable it.

6) Press the reload button and close the preferences dialog.

